Miss Jenny asks for Nia to bring more stone from the quarry but even that load goes missing, not long after Jack unloads it. Where could it have gone to? Everyone soon finds the answer and the outcome is also quite convenient for both the pack and Brenda.

programme.title: Leo the Wildlife Ranger
programme.desc: A stinky Hero seeks grooming advice from the Ring-tailed Lemurs.

programme.title: Leo the Wildlife Ranger
programme.desc: The Junior Rangers help Peyo befriend a Llama.

programme.title: Postman Pat Special Delivery Service
programme.desc: Julian and the kids at Greendale School are excited about a Festival of flight - Ted’s coming to talk about aviation and Alf’s bringing Cedric the racing pigeon. Pat has to deliver special jet boots to the school, built by Ted’s inventor friend. Ted will demonstrate them. But on the way to Greendale, Pat stops to help Alf, whose cows have got loose. Pat sees Ajay, out for a day’s bird-watching. Pat has promised to lend Ajay his wellies and asks Ajay to get them from the van, but Ajay takes the jet boots by mistake.

programme.title: Postman Pat Special Delivery Service
programme.desc: Pat tries to deliver to the school and find a new lamb on Greendale Fell at the same time.

programme.title: Bing Bunny
programme.desc: Bing and Sula are having so much fun playing together, they dont want to say goodbye.

programme.title: Bing Bunny
programme.desc: When Bing accidentally leaves his Hoppity Voosh toy at the park, Amma helps Bing focus and retrace his steps to find it.

programme.title: Bing Bunny
programme.desc: Bing and Flop are finally ready to leave for their picnic just as it starts to rain.

programme.title: Bing Bunny
programme.desc: Bing and Sula invent a noisy game with a helium balloon they find stuck in a tree.

programme.title: Bing Bunny
programme.desc: Coco discovers Bing’s dressing up box so they both dress up. Coco is Princess Cococapono and Bing is, of course, King Bing. But there is only one crown and both need it to complete their outfits. When the crown gets broken Flop helps them to make new crowns out of the broken pieces.

programme.title: Oswald
programme.desc: Pongo, a loveable Chinese dragon, becomes Oswalds best friend after Oswald helps him out of a tough spot. But Pongo is so big and clumsy he creates havoc. Pongo decides he just doesnt belong, but Oswald shows him that clumsy or not, Pongo fits in wherever he is.

programme.title: Oswald
programme.desc: Oswald and Weenie are preparing to race in the Big City Go-Kart Race. But Oswald is so busy helping his friends get ready, he misses the start. He trails, but catches up quickly as everyone else’s go-karts fall apart. Oswald gives them all a lift and they cross the finish line together to share first prize - a trophy full of ice cream.

programme.title: Bob the Builder
programme.desc: Bob is looking after Curtis’s garage while Leo takes him out for a birthday meal at Chef Tattie’s. However, the meal is a ruse, arranged so that Bob and his gang can secretly give Curtis’ workshop a makeover. Scoop is excited to be at the garage; he claims to have a great knowledge of mechanics. The build is all on schedule until Bob is forced to attend to Mr Bentley who keeps him busy because he’s very fussy about how much air he has in Philip’s tyres. At the restaurant Curtis is keen to get back to the garage as he is nervous about leaving it in somebody else’s hands. When Bob rings Leo and asks him to play for time Leo orders more and more food for himself to eat. At the, now busy, garage Scoop decides to take a look at what’s troubling Betsy, using the new vehicle inspection lift.

programme.title: Bob the Builder
programme.desc: Bob and the team are building Spring City’s new Ice Rink when the Rockets arrive and plead with him to finish it as soon as possible. They explain that the rink they were going to be playing on that evening is out of action and they have no-where to play! Bob tells them he’ll do his best and the building begins. Muck is fascinated by the idea of Ice Hockey and when Bob and Wendy set off to get the clear plastic panels to fit in the barrier surrounds, Muck decides to have a little go himself. Despite Leo’s protestations, all the machines are soon skidding about on the ice causing mayhem! When Bob and Wendy arrive back, they are alarmed to see all the barriers knocked down! Muck says sorry but Bob knows that the Rockets will be back very soon and they need to work fast.

programme.title: Guess How Much I Love You
programme.desc: One Autumn day Little Nutbrown Hare and Little Field Mouse convince Little Grey Squirrel to leave his pile of spotted acorns unattended, so they can all play with the crunchy leaves. While they’re gone Little Redwood Fox discovers the yummy acorns and takes them home. Once she finds out they actually belong Little Grey Squirrel, she has to decide whether to give them back or keep them.

programme.title: Guess How Much I Love You
programme.desc: The first snowfall of the Winter blankets the entire meadow, and Little Nutbrown Hare is confused because he can no longer see the bush, the log or his seedpod ball under all the snow! Will Little Nutbrown Hare be able to find his way around the meadow now that all his familiar places are covered under a blanket of fresh white snow?

programme.title: Guess How Much I Love You
programme.desc: On a snowy Winter’s morning Little Nutbrown Hare and Little Field Mouse are amazed at the intricate patterns they find in the snowflakes, each one different from the others. The friends try to take one to show Big Nutbrown Hare, but they always melt before he sees them. Will they find a way to stop the lovely flakes from melting?

programme.title: Learning Time With Timmy
programme.desc: It’s dressing up time and Timmy plays Doctor! Poor Teddy is sick, can you help Timmy put some plasters on Teddy to make him better?

programme.title: Hurray for Huckle!
programme.desc: The kids find some numbered papers blowing around the park. After investigating several possibilities of where they could be from, they finally figure out they were once fastened to trees in the park as part of a self-guided tour to celebrate Arbor Day. / When all the milk in Huckle’s Dad’s store turns out to be sour, Huckle, Sally and Lowly set out to find out why.

programme.title: Messy Goes To Okido
programme.desc: In the real world, Messy is running around. He runs so fast that he can feel his heart beating loudly! Why is that happening all of a sudden? "When you need to know, go to Okido!" Messy lands in Okido onto Zoe and Felixs trampoline. They all jump off, and they notice all their hearts are beating loudly but they don’t know why... Zim and Zam will know though, so off they go to see them. Zim, Zam and Zoom are baking a cake. Zim startles as they enter the lab, he was whisking so fast that his cake mix flies out of his hands and lands all over Zoom!

programme.title: Messy Goes To Okido
programme.desc: In the real world, Messy is having fun on his swing. Back and forth he goes but suddenly it breaks! A disappointed Messy goes off go to Okido to find out why! He lands in Felix and Zoes garden but cant see them anywhere. To Messy’s surprise, out they jump from behind something strange… “Where did these metal trees come from?” Messy asks them and discovers that they arent trees, theyre legs! In fact, theyre legs of Stan Tall, Okidos biggest robot who is helping Zim build a bridge today. So Messy whistles the Okidoodle over and they race Stan to the seaside to get started!

programme.title: Strawberry Shortcakes Berry Bitty Adventures
programme.desc: The twins birthday is approaching. Sour says she does not wish to share the birthday with Sweet. Sweet is sad that her sister feels that way but respects her wish. Sour initially enjoys having a birthday of her own and the activities the Berry girls plan for her, but gradually feels lonely without her sister, and regrets what she said earlier.

programme.title: Harry And His Bucket Full Of Dinosaurs
programme.desc: Harry is disappointed to find that he is not able to join in with any of the activities his family are taking part in at home.

programme.title: Harry And His Bucket Full Of Dinosaurs
programme.desc: When Harry is told to tidy his room he simply transfers all the mess into Dino-world, where he is told there is a no tidying up rule.

programme.title: Leo the Wildlife Ranger
programme.desc: Leo, Katie and Hero travel to Peru to take a marvellous spatuletail home. But what can they do when the hungry bird falls into a deep sleep?

programme.title: Thomas and Friends
programme.desc: The first time Samson came to Sodor he got lost. But Samson is a very proud engine and he doesn’t like to admit his mistakes. So he finds it very hard to listen to the other engines trying to warn him that he is making a mistake again when he accidentally takes Gordon’s Express Coaches to the quarry, instead of the trucks used for carrying stone.

programme.title: Thomas and Friends
programme.desc: When Scruff breaks down and has to be sent to the Steamworks, Samson is given the job of collecting up the track-side scrap. But Samson ends up taking his new responsibilities a little too seriously and collects up everything from the postman’s bike to the Fat Controller’s car. The Fat Controller has to race off to save it before it ends up getting crunched by Reg’s claw!

programme.title: Grisu
programme.desc: Some sheeps escaped from Mr. Guellecs field. The farmer is torn as he cant watch the herd and fix the broken fence which allows the sheep to run away at the same time.Its a perfect mission for Grisu who will learn to be a shepherd, with Stellas help. But the task isnt a piece of cake since the sheep dont want to listen to him at all. They rush away throughout the streets of Dragontown, causing troubles. Grisu and Stella have to discover how to steer a herd, especially a stubborn black sheep. Not an easy mission but as ever, a fire fighter never gives up!

programme.title: Grisu
programme.desc: The Dragon Stone, a beautiful and rare stone that Grisus ancestors found centuries ago breaks accidently. It was supposed to be the main stone of an exhibition that Professor Smeraldo has set up. To avoid cancelling the exhibition, Grisu, Fume and Stella go to explore a cave where they might find another legendary Dragon Stone. But the expedition turns into an adventure when they realize that only the two kids are able to go through the very small entrance of the cave. The quest quickly appears to be a big task for such young kids, even if one of them is a dragon. But thanks to their tenacity (fire-fighters never give up!), Grisu and Stella will be able to find the legendary stone and to find their way back. The exhibition will be saved!

programme.title: Guess How Much I Love You
programme.desc: Among the newly fallen Autumn leaves Little Nutbrown Hare finds a very peculiar little, hairy, green… ‘something’. Intrigued by what it might be Little Nutbrown Hare asks all his friends, but they all have different answers! It is certainly a very useful ‘something’, great for back scratching and games but it takes Little Grey Squirrel to solve the mystery.

programme.title: The Lost Paradise, a portrait of Arvo Part
programme.desc: He is the most performed contemporary composer in the world. Nevertheless, he also rarely ventures out in public, keeps quiet about his music, feels at home in the forests of Estonia and generates therewith – perhaps involuntarily – the impression of a recluse, which is attributed to him again and again: Arvo Part.The Estonian composer, who will celebrate his 90th birthday on September 11, 2025, verily exudes even solely by his appearance an aura of a mystic or an ascetic. He himself says: “I am no prophet, no cardinal, not a monk, not even a vegetarian.” But he is without a doubt a devout man, who has been a member of the Russian Orthodox Church since 1970, and under pressure from the Soviet apparatus of power was forced to leave his native Estonia in 1980. Via Vienna he arrived in Berlin, which for the next 30 years would become his second home and also the starting point for his international career.“The Lost Paradise” is the first international documentary about Arvo Part. It is quite an astonishment that such a shy artist has given his consent to be accompanied by a camera for an entire year: In his native Estonia, travelling to Germany, Italy, and Japan, where Part received the Praemium Imperiale, the world’s most prestigious award in the field of music, in October 2014.The film is framed by the identically named stage production “Adam’s Passion,” featuring three key works by Arvo Part, which American director Robert Wilson brought to the stage in May 2015 in a former submarine factory, the “Noblessner Foundry” in Tallinn.

programme.title: Beskyddare av egyptens skatter

programme.desc: CBP Nogales hittar kokain I stotfångaren på en bil som anlander från Mexiko, och CBP Atlanta stoppar en kvinna som smugglar valpar från Brasilien.

programme.title: Europa från ovan
programme.desc: Det forsta avsnittet av den andra sasongen i National Geographics dokumentarserie agnas åt Sverige. Historia, kultur, stader och naturfenomen och visar upp de foranderliga årstidernas hapnadsvackande skonhet.

programme.title: Car S.O.S
programme.desc: Car SOS står infor en tuff utmaning nar de ska restaurera en sallsynt Wolseley Hornet från 1934. Med delar som ar nastan omojliga att hitta och ingen instruktionsbok att luta sig mot måste teamet forlita sig på gammaldags hantverk och experttillverkning for att blåsa nytt liv i denna en gång bortglomda parla och ta den från en bortglomd relik till vagens konung. programme.title: Car S.O.S
programme.desc: Car SOS tar sig an en VW Polo G40 från 1991. Denna kompressormatade hot hatch tillhor 43-årige Anthony, vars forhoppningar om att få kora denna ikoniska bil grusades av en underkand besiktning 2007. Medan Fuzz återstaller bilens mekaniska hjarta reser Tim till Tyskland for att ta reda på historien bakom VW:s beslut att tillverka en Polo med kompressor. Var det ett djarvt drag att upphoja Polo till kungligheterna inom hot hatch?

programme.title: Engineering Europe
programme.desc: På en spannande resa genom Spaniens anmarkningsvarda tekniska underverk får vi en inblick i den banbrytande teknik som for Barcelonas Sagrada Familia narmare fardigstallandet. Darefter avslojar vi hemligheterna bakom Sevillas rekordstora solskydd i tra och besoker en skyskrapa som tycks trotsa tyngdkraften. Slutligen får vi bevittna den intrikata restaureringen av en 2 000 år gammal romersk teater.

programme.title: Engineering Europe
programme.desc: Vi avslojar Polens djarvaste tekniska underverk, ser en superhamn resa sig från havets djup, avslojar de anmarkningsvarda designhemligheterna bakom byggandet av EU:s hogsta byggnad, utforskar en vidstrackt underjordisk saltgruva och besoker varldens hogsta trakonstruktion, som ar 111 meter hog.

programme.title: Ice Road Rescue
programme.desc: Denna vinter stalls vintervagarnas hjaltar infor rent otroliga forhållanden. En unik storm och rekorderliga regn- och snomangder genererar enorma utmaningar. Nar de stalls infor karriarens tuffaste utmaningar måste Thord och Bjoern forlita sig på varandra som aldrig forr. I norr behover o Roger att fjolårets nykomling Stig tar nasta steg och blir raddningsledare - men ar han redo?

programme.title: Ice Road Rescue
programme.desc: I sodra Norge tvingas Thord, Bjoern och deras man ut i en av det senaste decenniets varsta stormar. De måste undsatta en lastbil full med stålbalkar, som stormvindar tvingat av vagen. Val på jobbet ger Bjoern Svein Arne en lektion i tyngdlagen. I norr skickar Jo Roger ut fjolårets nykomling, Stig på hans forsta solouppdrag for sasongen.

programme.title: Ice Road Rescue
programme.desc: Bjoern hamnar under press nar en frontalkrock mellan två lastbilar blockerar en ambulans under en nodutryckning. Thord jobbar hela natten for att undsatta en forare som sitter fast i sin lastbil och måste få sin last till flygplatsen i tid. I norr overvakar Stig undsattningen av en 30 ton tung lastbil som kort rakt igenom sakerhetsstaketet och hamnar farligt nara en elstolpe.

programme.title: Ice Road Rescue
programme.desc: Thord and Bjoern face the ultimate rescue challenge when a fully loaded truck crashes 40 metres down a mountainside and is completely destroyed. The gruelling conditions and complex logistics make this rescue one of the biggest challenges of their careers. In a nearby ski resort, Svein Arne is on a solo mission to rescue a delivery van that’s taken a very wrong turn.

programme.title: Ice Road Rescue
programme.desc: Bjoern stalls infor en svår situation nar en dubbelolycka tvingar honom att be sina rivaler om hjalp. På bergets andra sida måste Thord undsatta en 14 ton tung traktor som hotar att valta in i en prima fastighet. Uppe i norr skickas Stig ut att barga en postbil från att falla utfor ett 25 meter djupt stup.

programme.title: Ice Road Rescue
programme.desc: Uppe i norr stalls Jo Rogers nyborjare infor det ultimata testet nar de ska undsatta tre fordon som hamnat utanfor vagen. Nar sedan bogserbilen sjunker ner i ett djupt dike ar katastrofen nara. I soder for Thord och Andrzej en kamp mot klockan i ett forsok att radda en kraschad buss. Efter att ha upptackt ett diesellackage inser de att raddningen skulle kunna gå upp i rok.

programme.title: Ice Road Rescue
programme.desc: Nar en enorm varulastbil kraschar på E6:an tar Jo Roger hjalp av sin gamle van och tidigare anstallde, Roger, som får gora comeback. I bergen i norr inser Thord och Andrzej hur det ar att behova undsattning nar två av deras uppdrag drabbas av allvarliga bakslag.

programme.title: Ice Road Rescue
programme.desc: Thord befinner sig i en knepig situation nar polisen satter stopp for en raddningsaktion.

programme.title: Construction Fails
programme.desc: Vi avslojar episka byggmissar och undersoker konstruktionsfel i rymdfarjan Columbia, varfor fartyg kolliderar med broar i Kina, dålig hotelldesign, en tornkollaps i Shanghai och vardelosa flygplatser.

programme.title: Beskyddare av egyptens skatter
programme.desc: Vi foljer arkeologer som soker efter drottning Kleopatras grav. En grupp undervattensarkeologer dyker i Medelhavet for att utforska ruinerna av det forntida Alexandria. Ett annat team tar med några 4 000-åriga mumier till ett sjukhus for en rontgenundersokning. Vi får också folja med på en tur genom ett nyligen upptackt tunnelnatverk som kanske kan leda till den siste faraons sista viloplats!

programme.title: Cleopatras Final Secret
programme.desc: Bevapnad med den senaste tekniken och med hjalp av havsutforskaren Bob Ballard soker arkeologen Kathleen Martinez på land och under vatten efter sitt livs upptackt – Kleopatras forsvunna grav.

programme.title: Beskyddare av egyptens skatter
programme.desc: Arkeologer undersoker forntida Egyptens mest kanda kvinnliga farao, Kleopatra. I Dendera upptacker vi hur Kleopatra utnyttjade egyptisk religion for att uppnå sina mål. På den antika platsen Philadelphia avslojar teamet en gammal kista och dyrbara gravgods for att lara sig mer om Kleopatras amnen. Och vid Taposiris Magna beger sig arkeologer under jorden for att soka efter Kleopatras forsvunna grav.

programme.title: Edge of the Unknown
programme.desc: Alex Honnold blev varldens mest beromde alpinist nar han besteg granitvaggen i Yosemite utan rep. Men hur forberedde sig Alex infor att gora det omojliga? Han och Tommy Caldwell for till Marocko och pressade sig till det yttersta på lika hoga vaggar, som kulminerade i Alex replosa klattring. Detta ar Alex outtrottliga, slitsamma process for att forvandla drommen till verklighet.

programme.title: Top Guns: The Next Generation
programme.desc: Nya officerare påborjar en elitutbildning till stridspiloter, men endast ett fåtal kommer att klara utbildningen. De kampar med precisionsbombning och utsatts for hårda bedomningar av instruktorerna.

programme.title: Ice Road Rescue
programme.desc: Under en natt med kaos, krascher och konvojer blir Thord upprord nar ett annat foretag tar sig in på hans territorium. I norr tar Ole Henrik med sig foretagets nya bargningsbil på dess forsta uppdrag att radda en lastbil som kraschat djupt ner i ett snotackt dike och sedan slagit runt 90 grader. Ole Henrik ar ivrig att testa den nya bargningsbilen for att se om den ar vard den stora investeringen.

programme.title: Engineering Europe
programme.desc: Vi avslojar Polens djarvaste tekniska underverk, ser en superhamn resa sig från havets djup, avslojar de anmarkningsvarda designhemligheterna bakom byggandet av EU:s hogsta byggnad, utforskar en vidstrackt underjordisk saltgruva och besoker varldens hogsta trakonstruktion, som ar 111 meter hog.

programme.title: Northwoods Survival
programme.desc: Margot ar mitt i vinterns djup och ger sig ut på jakt efter vardefulla palsdjur; Billy ar fast besluten att trivas i de kalla skogarna i norr och forsoker sig på att bygga ett uppvarmningssystem for varmvatten. Matty gor några rejala ”komfort”-uppgraderingar i sin nyligen utbyggda bostad på Newfoundland. Och nar Emilie och Gilbert tar en paus från stugbyggandet agnar de sig åt att sakra en traditionell och viktig matkalla.

programme.title: Familier som våre
programme.desc: Laura bygger et nytt liv uten Elias. Når de endelig møtes igjen, er han en skygge av seg selv, men Laura gir ikke opp håpet om å bringe ham tilbake.

programme.title: Vikingane
programme.desc: Fungerende høvding Orm må vike for broren Olav, som vender tilbake fra tokt, og blir ikke engang invitert til kveldens plyndringsfest.

programme.title: Vikingane
programme.desc: Rufus fra Roma sliter med å finne seg til rette i sin nye rolle som trell og trives ikke med livssituasjonen i Norheim. Den positive trellen Kark er institusjonalisert og prøver å legge livet til rette for Rufus. Det nye livet som gårdseier og ektemann blir ikke helt som Arvid forestilte seg. Jakten på en rømt trell avdekker stor magi, vekker interessen for nytenking i landsbyen og former nye vennskap. En hendelse på dostanga tar landsbyen i en ny dramatisk vending.

programme.title: Singelgåten
programme.desc: Det har vært ubehagets år, og det er på tide å se om all innsatsen har gitt resultater.

programme.desc: Paranoia, spionasje, misbruk og svik – dette er den spinnville historia om tenåringen Siggi, som vart Julian Assange si høgre hand i Wikileaks.

programme.desc: Shakespeares familie henges ut som katolikker, og dermed forrædere. Selv skriver han sitt mest episke og tragiske verk.

programme.desc: Benedikt talar til Altingi om psykisk helse. Både politiske spenningar og familiekonfliktar eskalerer.

programme.desc: Mathias nærmer seg en beslutning. Erik har allerede truffet sin, men kanskje den var feil?

programme.desc: Småbarnsmora Louise flyttar til USA og oppdagar at skulane øver på skyteepisodar. No ønskjer ho å lære meir om dei kontroversielle tryggleiksrutinane.

programme.desc: Christine tar Girl in Red med på en biltur fylt med overraskelser og musikk. Hun vil finne ut hvordan en nokså redd artist fra Horten har klart å vinne verden med musikken sin.

programme.title: Rauða borðið 25. sept - Rettur er settur, rauði þráðurinn, Taoismi og klassíkin rokkar - NÝR ÞÁTTUR
programme.desc: Gísli Tryggvason logmaður fer yfir mannrettindi, Bokun 35, kynþáttamisretti og fleira í samtali við Bjorn Þorláksson. Kolbeinn H. Stefánsson dosent í felagsráðgjof ræðir við Gunnar Smára um vanda vinstrisins á Vesturlondum og her heima. Ragnar Baldursson Kínaserfræðingur heldur áfram að skýra fyrir Gunnari Smára hvernig taoisminn hefur motað Kína, menningu og stjornmál, og hugmyndir Kínverja um stoðu Kína í heiminum. Kristinn Sigmundsson bassi, Kolbeinn Ketilsson tenor og Matthildur Anna Gísladottir píanoleikari ræða um ljoðasong við Gunnar Smára og tonlistarnemana Soleyju Lou Smáradottur og Sol Bjornsdottur, um operu, tofra tonlistar, kvíða fyrir tonleika, íslenska einsongslagið og margt fleira.

programme.title: Næturdagskrá Samstoðvarinnar
programme.desc: Næturdagskrá Samstoðvarinnar

programme.title: Rauða borðið 24. sept - Palestína, húsnæðiskrísa, Trump, taoismi og heyskapur - ENDURSÝNT
programme.desc: Gunnar Smári ræðir við Hilmar Þor Hilmarsson professor um stefnubreytingu Trump gagnvart Úkraínu, sem hann segir nú að geti unnið stríð. Þeir fara líka yfir ræðu Trump í alsherjarþinginu, elta hana um víðan voll. Alvarleg staða er uppi í húsnæðismálum fjolmargra einstaklinga án þess að það fari hátt í samfelaginu. Fordomar eru miklir og harka í samfelaginu. María Petursdottir oryrki og myndlistarkona og Styrmir Hallsson, háskolanemi og ungur maður í leit að oruggu framtíðarhúsnæði, ræða ástandið með Birni Þorláks. Vorstjarnan heldur fund um málið annað kvold. Þordís Ingadottir lagaprofessor ræðir við Gunnar Smára um gildi þess að fleiri lond viðurkenna nú Palestínu, um hvort alþjoðalog og alþjoðakerfið se að veikjast vegna stefnu Bandaríkjanna og hvaða skyldur íslensk stjornvold bera frammi fyrir þjoðarmorði á Gaza og oðrum glæpum Ísraelsstjornar. Ragnar Baldursson Kínafræðingur ræðir við Gunnar Smára um Taoisma og áhrif hans á kínverska menningu, stefnu kínverska ríkisins og einnig um áhrif Tao á vestræna menningu. Þetta er fyrri hluti spjalls þeirra um Taoisma. Til marks um sprettusumarið sem nú er að baki eru dæmi um bændur á Norðurlandi sem slogu tún sín fjorum sinnum, sem er einsdæmi að sogn Trausta Þorissonar, bonda á Hofsá. Bjorn Þorláks slær á þráðinn norður.

programme.title: Skvíz
programme.desc: Nútíma saga þriggja kvenna sem leigja saman íbúð í Reykjavík og reyna að feta hver sína leið í vinnu, ástum og ollu þar á milli. Þær eru allar mannlegar og misheppnaðar á sinn hátt en hjálpa hvor annarri í gegnum olíkar lífsreynslur að finna kraftinn sinn.

programme.title: Station 19
programme.desc: Dramatísk þáttaroð um slokkviliðsfolk í Seattle sem hættir lífi sínu til að bjarga oðrum, á meðan personulegt líf þeirra er í uppnámi. Þættirnir eru frá framleiðendum Greys Anatomy.

programme.title: FBI
programme.desc: After a front-running female presidential candidate, Valerie Caldwell, is targeted with a car bomb, OA and Maggie must hurry to track down the bomber before they strike again. The case leads them to wonder whether this person is targeting Caldwell for her political aspirations or something else.

programme.title: FBI: Most Wanted
programme.desc: Bandarísk þáttaroð um liðsmenn bandarísku alríkislogreglunnar, FBI, sem eltast við hættulegustu glæpamenn Bandaríkjanna.

programme.title: Sweetpea
programme.desc: Bresk spennuþáttaroð um Rhiannon Lewis, skrifstofustúlku sem lítið fer fyrir og fáir taka eftir. Einn daginn fær hún nog og byrjar að myrða folkið sem hefur komið illa fram við hana.

programme.title: The Chi
programme.desc: Bandarísk þáttaroð frá Emmy-verðlaunahafanum Lena Waithe. Lífið í suðurhluta Chicago tekur á sig ýmsar myndir. Þættir sem hafa hlotið mikið lof gagnrýnenda.

programme.title: Tonlist
programme.desc: Bandarísk gamanþáttaroð með Cedric the Entertainer í aðalhlutverki. Hann leikur fjolskyldufoður í rotgronu hverfi blokkumanna í Los Angeles sem bregður í brún þegar hann kynnist nýju nágronnunum.

programme.title: Love Island
programme.desc: Bráðskemmtileg raunveruleikasería þar sem eldheitir einstaklingar fá tækifæri til að finna ástina í fjorugum leik.

programme.title: The King of Queens
programme.desc: Þegar Doug fær slæma tannpínu og þarf að fá rotfyllingu kemst hann að því að Carrie var einu sinni skotin í tannlækninum hans.

programme.title: Top Chef
programme.desc: Top Chef heldur nú til Kanada þar sem fimmtán nýir keppendur mæta spenntir til leiks.

programme.title: The Prince And Me: The Elephant Adventure
programme.desc: Ár er liðið síðan Edvard konungur (Chirs Geere) og Paige drottning (Kam Heskin) af Danmorku giftu sig. Þeim er boðið til brúðkaups prinsessunnar Myru af Sangyoon. Þegar komið er á áfangastað kemst Paige að því að Myra er alls ekki sátt við ráðahaginn og vill ekki giftast hinum kaldlynda Kah, heldur elskar á laun hinn unga fílahirði Alu. Þegar upp kemst um leynilegt ástarsamband þeirra Myru og Alu er fílahirðinum unga skellt í fangelsi. Þá hverfur hinn heilagi brúðkaups-fíll og Paige og Edvard þurfa að leggja á sig ferðalag inn í frumskoginn til að finna fílinn og bjarga Alu úr fangelsi svo hægt se að sannfæra konginn af Sangyoon að ástin er ollum máttarvoldum æðri.

programme.title: Bachelor in Paradise
programme.desc: Bandarísk raunveruleikasería þar sem fyrrum þátttakendur í The Bachelor og The Bachelorette fá annað tækifæri til að finna ástina og kanna ný ástarsambond.

programme.title: Midway
programme.desc: Myndin dregur nafn sitt af samnefndri sjoorrustu á milli Bandaríkjanna og Japans í heimsstyrjoldinni síðari sem átti ser stað vestan við Midway-eyju á Kyrrahafi 4.–7. júní 1942.

programme.title: Kidnapping Mr. Heineken
programme.desc: Forsagan að skipulagningu, framkvæmd, eftirmála og að lokum endalokum mannræningja bjormogúlsins Alfred "Freddy" Heineken, en greitt var hæsta lausnargjald sem nokkurn tímann hefur verið greitt fyrir einstakling, í þessu máli. Þann 9. november árið 1983 var Alfred Heineken, eiganda bjorveldisins, rænt fyrir framan hofuðstoðvar fyrirtækisins í Amsterdam. Ránið var framkvæmt af fjorum monnum sem hofðu ásamt fimmta manninum skipulagt það í tvo ár áður en þeir letu til skarar skríða. Í myndinni er farið yfir málið frá upphafi til enda, allt frá því að hugmyndin kom upp í kolli forsprakka mannræningjanna þar til þeir voru dæmdir fyrir glæpinn, en Heineken-fjolskyldan ákvað að greiða lausnarfeð, þvert á vilja logreglunnar, sem um leið varð hæsta upphæð sem nokkurn tíma hafði verið greidd í mannránsmáli.

programme.title: Colette
programme.desc: Sidonie-Gabrielle Colette fæddist árið 1873 og giftist árið 1893 rithofundinum og útgefandanum Henry Gauthier-Villars. Hann hvatti hana til að skrifa sogur og úr varð að Colette skrifaði fjorar bækur um unglingsstúlkuna Claudine sem urðu mjog vinsælar. Vandamálið var að Henry hafði gefið sogurnar út í eigin nafni og við það gat Colette ekki sætt sig til lengdar.

programme.title: Halo
programme.desc: Spennandi þáttaroð úr smiðju Steven Spielberg þar sem personulegar sogur, spenna og hasar tvinnast saman.

programme.title: Tonlist
programme.desc: Bandarísk gamanþáttaroð með Cedric the Entertainer í aðalhlutverki. Hann leikur fjolskyldufoður í rotgronu hverfi blokkumanna í Los Angeles sem bregður í brún þegar hann kynnist nýju nágronnunum.

programme.title: Olís deild kvenna
programme.desc: Bein útsending frá leik Hauka og Fram í Olís deild kvenna.

programme.title: Love Island
programme.desc: Bráðskemmtileg raunveruleikasería þar sem eldheitir einstaklingar fá tækifæri til að finna ástina í fjorugum leik.

programme.title: The King of Queens
programme.desc: The fourth season concludes with Arthur visiting a psychiatrist and recalling via flashback a disturbing encounter with his dad that may explain Arthurs abrasive personality.

programme.title: The Real Love Boat Australia
programme.desc: Skemmtilegur stefnumotaþáttur þar sem ástleitnir einstaklingar fá tækifæri til að finna storu ástina með því að taka þátt í skemmtilegum leik um borð í skemmtiferðaskipi.

programme.title: Tough As Nails
programme.desc: Phil Keoghan úr Amazing Race stýrir spennandi keppni þar sem hversdagslegar hetjur keppa í raunverulegum aðstæðum.

programme.title: Poppa’s House
programme.desc: Gamanþáttur með Wayans feðgum í aðalhlutverki um fúllynda útvarpsmanninn Poppa og fullorðinn son hans, sem reynir að elta drauma sína á sama tíma og hann sinnir fjolskyldunni.

programme.title: Florence Foster Jenkins
programme.desc: Bresk sannsoguleg gamanmynd frá 2016 með Meryl Streep í hlutverki hefðarfrúarinnar Florence Foster Jenkins sem er staðráðin í að láta draum sinn um að verða operusongkona rætast þrátt fyrir að hafa litla sem enga songhæfileika. Leikstjori: Stephen Frears. Önnur hlutverk: Hugh Grant, Simon Helberg og Rebecca Ferguson.

programme.title: Ali And Ava
programme.desc: Tvær einmana sálir ná djúpri tengingu og þurfa í kjolfarið að gera upp fyrri sambond sem hanga enn yfir þeim. Einnig þurfa þau að koma hreint fram við fjolskyldur sínar þar sem margt er enn osagt.

programme.title: Tag Min Hand
programme.desc: Maja reynir að ná tokum á lífi sínu og komast að því hver hún er án eiginmannsins síns eftir að hann oskar skyndilega eftir skilnaði.

programme.title: 21 Bridges
programme.desc: Horkuspennandi glæpamynd frá 2019 með Chadwick Boseman, Siennu Miller og J.K. Simmons í aðalhlutverkum.Andre Davis er logregluforingi í New York sem kvold eitt er kallaður til vettvangsrannsoknar þar sem átta logreglumenn hafa verið skotnir til bana með oflugum velbyssum.
